title: George Clinton - Hey Man... Smell My Finger@flac
description:
Hey Man, Smell My Finger is everything a great George Clinton album should be -- conceptually disjointed, overlong, silly, sloppy, and funky as hell. 
Thankfully, the music here is his best since Computer Games, and the album proves just how responsible he is for much of the music of the 1990s, as the irresistible single "Paint the White House Black" illustrates with its numerous cameos. (AMG)
